rld-nda-modi%5C%22%3EJayant%20Choudhary%20but%20expressed%20satisfaction%20that%20he%20was%20aligning%20with%20Modi.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20boasted%20about%20their%20knowledge%20of%20history%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CBabar%20and%20Aurangzeb%20demolished%20temples%20and%20built%20mosques.%20Modi%20is%20building%20a%20temple.%20That%E2%80%99s%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20proclaimed%20proudly%2C%20almost%20in%20unison.%20Some%20emphasised%20their%20connection%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20Maharana%20Pratap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20about%20Hakim%20Khan%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Maharana%20who%20met%20martyrdom%20fighting%20valorously%20against%20the%20Mughal%20army%20at%20the%20battle%20of%20Haldighati%20in%201576%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20man%2C%20tearing%20open%20a%20sachet%20of%20gutkha%2C%20popped%20its%20contents%20into%20his%20mouth%2C%20and%20looked%20at%20his%20mobile%20phone%20screen.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHis%20name%20was%20Hakim%20Khan%2C%20but%20he%20was%20a%20Rajput%2C%20not%20a%20Muslim.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20shared%20sweets%20among%20themselves.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09184958%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-6.47.54.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221084%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09184958%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-6.47.54.png%201084w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09184958%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-6.47.54-300x268.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09184958%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-6.47.54-1024x914.png%2010