rms%20By%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20a%20special%20address%20in%20Parliament%20this%20evening%20--%20his%20last%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20--%20said%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20%26quot%3Bachieved%20what%20generations%20waited%20for%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20its%20last%20session%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20five%20years%20were%20about%20reform%2C%20perform%20and%20transform%20in%20country...%20Many%20reforms%2C%20that%20were%20game-changers%2C%20happened%20during%20this%20year%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20%26quot%3Bmoving%20towards%20a%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20citing%20multiple%20issues%20from%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20penalising%20Triple%20Talaq%20to%20hosting%20the%20prestigious%20G20%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20list%2C%20which%20also%20included%20Data%20protection%20bill%2C%20stringent%20laws%20to%20fight%20terror%2C%20removal%20of%20obsolete%20laws%20and%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20as%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20--%20started%20with%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20and%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20parliament%20library%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20said%20we%20needed%20a%20new%20building.%20Everyone%20wanted%20it%2C%20but%20there%20was%20never%20a%20decision%20on%20it.%20We%20decided%20on%20it%20and%20owing%20to%20that%20we%20are%20sitting%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20of%20the%20focus%20on%20marginalised%20people%20including%20transgenders%2C%2017%2C000%20of%20whom%20%26quot%3Breceived%20identity%20cards%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20gave%20Padma%20awards%20to%20transgenders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20th