%20of%20Guwahati%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20as%20baseless.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20threat%20and%20I%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20this%20is%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20UCA%20News%2C%20adding%20that%20legal%20means%20would%20be%20explored%20to%20address%20such%20open%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20ultimatum%2C%20Christian%20leaders%20have%20advised%20priests%2C%20nuns%2C%20and%20brothers%20to%20wear%20civil%20Indian%20dresses%20on%20campuses%20as%20a%20precaution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristian%20leaders%20plan%20to%20approach%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20to%20address%20the%20threats%20posed%20to%20Christianity%20and%20missionary%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristian%20leaders%20say%20threats%20to%20Christianity%20and%20missionary%20activities%20have%20increased%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20the%20entire%20northeast%20India%20region%20after%20Hindu%20groups%20began%20to%20push%20cultural%20nationalism.%20The%20Hindu%20groups%20have%20succeeded%20in%20portraying%20Christianity%20as%20a%20diabolical%20force%20to%20destroy%20Hindu%20native%20culture%20and%20to%20convert%20Hindus%20to%20Christianity%2C%20the%20UCA%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20Christians%20make%20up%203.74%20percent%20of%20the%20population%2C%20exceeding%20the%20national%20average%20of%202.3%20percent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20(UCF)%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20organisation%20focused%20on%20Christian%20issues%2C%20had%20released%20a%20statement%20last%20year%20highlighting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3Ethe%20rise%20in%20attacks%20against%20the%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%2