.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%20(2014)%2C%20the%20economy%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20shape.%20There%20were%20scams%20everywhere.%20Foreign%20investment%20was%20not%20coming.%20Had%20we%20taken%20out%20a%20white%20paper%20at%20that%20time%2C%20it%20would%20have%20given%20a%20wrong%20message%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20after%2010%20years%2C%20our%20government%20has%20revived%20the%20economy%2C%20brought%20foreign%20investment%20and%20there%20is%20no%20corruption%20at%20all.%20So%20it%20is%20the%20right%20time%20to%20publish%20the%20white%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhyas-ram-temple-receives-rs-11-crore-in-donations-since-grand-opening-4978723%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERam%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20said%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20believed%20for%20500-550%20years%20that%20the%20temple%20should%20be%20built%20at%20the%20place%20where%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20due%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20appeasement%20and%20citing%20law%20and%20order%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20was%20not%20allowed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20the%20law%2C%20enacted%20in%202019%2C%20will%20be%20implemented%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20after%20issuing%20the%20rules%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Muslim%20brothers%20are%20being%20misled%20and%20instigated%20(against%20the%20CAA).%20The%20CAA%20is%20only%20meant%20to%20give%20citizenship%20to%20those%20who%20came%20to%20India%20after%20facing%20persecution%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20It%20is%20not%20for%20snatching%20anyone's%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F