a%20like%20three%20other%20cheetahs%2C%20Union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20said%20in%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20question%20posed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20no%20other%20details%20were%20known%20about%20Shaurya%E2%80%99s%20death%20except%20that%20the%20animal%20died%20despite%20being%20treated%20for%20%E2%80%9Cweakness%E2%80%9D.%20Officials%20had%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20could%20be%20ascertained%20only%20once%20the%20post-mortem%20results%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20still%20awaited%20%E2%80%93%20came%20in.%20The%20reply%20by%20Yadav%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20say%20what%20caused%20Shaurya%20or%20the%20other%20three%20cheetahs%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20septicemia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShaurya%20is%20the%20seventh%20adult%20cheetah%20to%20die%20so%20far%2C%20and%20the%20most%20recent%20death%20among%20the%2020%20cheetahs%20that%20were%20originally%20brought%20to%20India%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20introduce%20the%20African%20cheetah%20into%20select%20grassland%20habitats%20in%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EVariation%20in%20causes%20of%20deaths%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%208%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20listed%20the%20causes%20due%20to%20which%20the%20seven%20adult%20cheetahs%20died%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%2C%20where%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20ongoing.%20The%20Minister%20listed%20this%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20regarding%20the%20Project%20by%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Bihar%20and%20a%20BJP%20leader.%20Modi%20inquired%20about%20the%20number%20of%20cubs%20born%20to%20cheetahs%20in%20Kuno%2C%20how%20many%20animals%20had%20died%20till%20now%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20their%20deaths%20in%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20high%20numbers%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20asked%20whether%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20till%20now%20is%20%E2%80%9Cusual%20or%20unusual%E2%80%9D%20in%20such%20cheetah%20relocation%20projects%2C%20and%20what%20efforts%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20to%20avoid%20more%20cheetah%20deaths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply%2C%20the%20cheetahs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Ffemale-cheetah-from-namibia-dies-in-mps-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESasha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fsecond-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park-in-less-than-one-month%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthird-african-cheetah-dies-in-india-five-to-be-released-in-kuno-soon%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDaksha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Crenal%20insufficiency%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cneurological%E2%80%9D%20issues%2C%20and%20during%20a%20%E2%80%9Cviolent%20encounter%20with%20a%20male%20coalition%20during%20a%20mating%20attempt%E2%80%9D%2C%20respectively.%20The%20four%20other%20adults%20%E2%80%93%20Tejas%2C%20Suraj%2C%20Dhatri%20and%20Shaurya%20%E2%80%93%20all%20died%20due%20to%20septicemia%2C%20per%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20some%20of%20these%20causes%20vary%20from%20a%20similar%20list%20submitted%20by%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20the%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20on%20July%2020%20last%20year%2C%20also%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Per%20Choubey%E2%80%99s%20submission%2C%20while%20Sasha%20died%20due%20to%20chronic%20renal%20or%20kidney%20failure%2C%20Daksha%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%20(as%20opposed%20to%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20latest%20list%20that%20puts%20it%20to%20a%20violent%20mating%20attempt)%2C%20and%20Uday%20died%20due%20to%20cardiopulmonary%20failure%20(as%20opposed%20to%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20most%20recent%20list%20that%20lists%20the%20cause%20of%20Uday%E2%80%99s%20death%20as%20%E2%80%9Cneurological%E2%80%9D).%20Officials%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20had%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcheetah-uday-dies-of-heart-attack-triggered-by-toxin-post-mortem-reveals-101682361675687.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20April%2025%20last%20year%20that%20as%20per%20the%20preliminary%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20Uday%20died%20due%20to%20cardiopulmonary%20failure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1.jpg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112349%2Frs1-1024x409.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22449%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20reasons%20for%20death%2C%20as%20submitted%20by%20Choubey%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20July%2020%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFour%20cheetahs%20died%20due%20to%20septicemia%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChoubey%20also%20said%20that%20Tejas%2C%20Suraj%20and%20Daksha%20died%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D.%20Yadav%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20su