3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(on%20July%2015%20last%20year)%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20were%20caused%20by%20septicaemia%2C%20an%20infection%20of%20the%20bloodstream%2C%20brought%20on%20by%20wounds%20caused%20by%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20abrasion%20of%20radio%20collars%20fitted%20on%20their%20necks%20and%20moisture%20accumulated%20under%20the%20collars.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20experts%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Suraj%E2%80%99s%20death%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpotentially%20avoidable%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20authorities%20lost%20%E2%80%9Ca%20full%20day%E2%80%9D%20in%20taking%20action%20while%20waiting%20for%20the%20post-mortem%20report%20of%20Tejas%2C%20the%20first%20cheetah%20to%20die%20of%20a%20neck%20wound%20on%20July%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%202%2C%20a%20press%20note%20released%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20forest%20department%20said%20that%20a%20monitoring%20team%20found%20Dhatri%2C%20a%20female%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20that%20morning.%20The%20animal%2C%20which%20authorities%20were%20trying%20to%20capture%20from%20the%20wild%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Surya%2C%20was%20then%20the%20sixth%20adult%20to%20die.%20In%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCCFCheetah%2Fstatus%2F1687116755548995584%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseries%20of%20tweets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20August%203%2C%20the%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%20(CCF)%20which%20has%20assisted%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20said%20that%20a%20post-mortem%20revealed%20that%20Dhatri%20died%20due%20to%20myiasis%2C%20or%20infection%20caused%20by%20fly%20larvae%20(maggots).%20As%20per%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20latest%20list%2C%20Dhatri%20died%20of%20septicemia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seventh%20death%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20recent%20so%20far%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20of%20Shaurya%2C%20a%20male%20from%20Namibia%2C%20on%20January%2016.%20Yadav%2C%20in%20his%20recent%20list%2C%20has%20also%20submitted%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20Shaurya%20too%20died%20of%20septicemia.%20The%20animal%2C%20housed%20in%20an%20enclosure%2C%20was%20treated%20for%20%E2%80%9Cweakness%E2%80%9D%20after%20it%20displayed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstaggering%20gait%E2%80%9D%2C%20officials%20had%20said.%20However%2C%20the%20animal%20died%20despite%20treatment.%20Officials%20had%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20could%20be%20ascertained%20only%20once%20the%20detailed%20post-mortem%20results%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced%20by%20the%20Ministry%20or%20the%20NTCA%20%E2%80%93%20came%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20ensure%20conservation%20and%20protection%20of%20Cheetahs%20in%20India%2C%20actions%20are%20taken%20as%20per%20scientific%20action%20plan%20prepared%20with%20inputs%20of%20leading%20Cheetah%20experts%20including%20biologists%2C%20ecologists%2C%20conservationists%20and%20managers.%20A%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20review%20progress%2C%20monitor%20and%20advise%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20introduction%20in%20consultation%20with%20international%20cheetah%20experts%2C%20as%20and%20when%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Action%20Plan%20for%20the%20introduction%20of%20Cheetah%2C%2012-14%20individuals%20per%20year%20are%20proposed%20to%20be%20brought%20from%20South%20Africa%20and%20Namibia%20or%20other%20African%20countries%20during%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20availability%20of%20animals%20and%20status%20of%20introduced%20cheetahs%2C%20Yadav%20said%20in%20his%20response%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20His%20reply%20also%20mentioned%20that%20actions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20introduce%20cheetahs%20into%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707544565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsepticemia-caused-deaths-of-four-cheetahs-union-environment-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adult%20male%20Shaurya%20that%20died%20on%20January%2016%20is%20the%20fourth%20cheetah%20to%20die%20due%20to%20septicemia%2C%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsepticemia-caused-deaths-of-four-cheetahs-union-environment-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20residents%20surviving%20off%20animal%20feed%20and%20rice%20as%20food%20dwindles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707544304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1320E%2Fproduction%2F_132605387_rtrrafahfood050224a00eac29801d15dc4e8311b3ced49092dffe4e2c0_594_4291_24151000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68239320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN%20says%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20in%20the%20territory%20are%20at%20growing%20risk%20of%20famine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2273%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68239320%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68239320.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%