day%20after%20the%20elections%20and%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20bring%20this%20country%20out%20of%20the%20whirlpool%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20told%20a%20crowd%20of%20supporters%20gathered%20outside%20his%20home%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20has%20got%20the%20mandate%2C%20whether%20independents%20or%20parties%2C%20we%20respect%20the%20mandate%20they%20have%20got%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20invite%20them%20to%20sit%20with%20us%20and%20help%20this%20wounded%20nation%20get%20back%20on%20its%20feet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%20released%20an%20audio-visual%20message%20created%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20shared%20on%20his%20X%20social%20media%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20message%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20delivered%20by%20word%20through%20his%20lawyers%2C%20Khan%2C%2071%2C%20rejected%20Sharif's%20claim%20to%20victory%2C%20congratulated%20his%20supporters%20on%20%26quot%3Bwinning%26quot%3B%20the%20election%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20celebrate%20and%20protect%20their%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20trusted%20that%20you%20all%20would%20come%20out%20to%20vote%20-%20and%20you%20honoured%20that%20trust%20and%20your%20massive%20turnout%20has%20shocked%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20said%2C%20adding%20no%20one%20would%20accept%20Sharif's%20claim%20because%20he%20had%20won%20fewer%20seats%20and%20because%20there%20had%20been%20rigging%20in%20the%20polls.Former%20cricket%20superstar%20Khan%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20August%2C%20and%20was%20convicted%20three%20times%20in%20six%20days%20in%20the%20leadup%20to%20the%20polls%20for%2010%2C%2014%20and%20seven%20years%20in%20cases%20related%20to%20state%20secrets%2C%20graft%20and%20an%20unlawful%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%2C%2074%2C%20a%20three-time%20former%20premier%2C%20returned%20from%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20late%20last%20year%2C%20having%20contested%20the%20last%20election%20from%20a%20jail%20cell%20on%20a%20graft%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20considered%20the%20front-runner%20to%20lead%20the%20country%2C%20having%20buried%20a%20long-running%20feud%20with%20the%20powerful%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20said%20his%20party%20would%20have%20preferred%20to%20win%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20own%20but%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20that%20would%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20others%2C%20including%20former%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20of%20PPP%2C%20to%20open%20negotiations%20as%20early%20as%20Friday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20reaction%2C%20a%20senior%20aide%20of%20Khan%20said%20PTI%20leaders%20would%20hold%20talks%20among%20themselves%20and%20also%20meet%20Khan%20in%20jail%20on%20Saturday%20to%20discuss%20the%20results%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20of%20the%20vote%20have%20been%20unusually%20delayed%2C%20which%20the%20caretaker%20government%20ascribed%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20phone%20services%20-%20a%20security%20measure%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20members%20cannot%20form%20a%20government%20on%20their%20own%20under%20Pakistan's%20complex%20election%20system%20which%20also%20includes%20reserved%20seats%20that%20will%20be%20allotted%20to%20parties%20based%20on%20their%20winnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20independents%20have%20the%20option%20to%20join%20any%20party%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20For%20Coalition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20timely%20announcement%20of%20the%20results%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20smooth%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20government%2C%20will%20reduce%20policy%20and%20political%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody's%20Investors%20Service%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20country%20that%20is%20facing%20very%20challenging%20macroeconomic%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20the%20announcement%20of%20results%20was%20unusual%20for%20Pakistan.%20Karachi's%20stock%20index%20and%20Pakistan's%20sovereign%20bonds%20fell%20because%20of%20the%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20electoral%20battle%20had%20been%20expected%20to%20be%20between%20candidates%20backed%20by%20Khan%2C%20whose%20PTI%20won%20the%20last%20national%20election%2C%20and%20the%20PML-N.%20Khan%20believes%20the%20powerful%20military%20is%20behind%20a%20crackdown%20to%20hound%20his%20party%20out%20of%20existence%2C%20while%20analysts%20and%20opponents%20say%20Sharif%20is%20being%20backed%20by%20the%20generals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20has%20dominated%20the%20nuclear-armed%20country%20either%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20in%20its%2076%20years%20of%20independence%20from%20Britain%20but%20for%20several%20years%20it%20has%20maintained%20it%20does%20not%20interfere%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20a%20coalition%20government%20will%20struggle%20to%20tackle%20multiple%20challenges%20-%20foremost%20being%20seeking%20a%20new%20bailout%20programme%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20after%20the%20current%20arrangement%20expires%20in%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20government%20%26quot%3Bwould%20probably%20be%20unstable%2C%20weak%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20big%20loser%20...%20will%20be%20the%20army%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Marvin%20Weinbaum%2C%20Director%20of%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan%20Studies%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%20Institute%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20army%20really%20has%20staked%20its%20reputation%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver%20this%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20was%20expected%20to%20help%20resolve%20the%20crises%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20but%20a%20fractured%20verdict%20%26quot%3Bcould%20very%20well%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20even%20deeper%20exposure%20to%20forces%20which%20would%20create%20instability%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707530340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3q33scao_nawaz-sharif-imran-khan_625x300_10_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboth-imran-khan-nawaz-sharif-declare-victory-as-pakistan-elections-results-drag-on-5029198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Pakistani%20prime%20ministers%20and%20bitter%20rivals%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20Imran%20Khan%20on%20Friday%20both%20declared%20victory%20in%20elections%20marred%20by%20delayed%20results%20and%20militant%20attacks%2C%20throwing%20the%20country%20into%20further%20political%20turmoil.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboth-imran-khan-nawaz-sharif-declare-victory-as-pakistan-elections-results-drag-on-5029198%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboth-imran-khan-nawaz-sharif-declare-victory-as-pakistan-elections-results-drag-on-5029198%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboth-imran-khan-nawaz-sharif-declare-victory-as-pakistan-elections-results-drag-on-5029198%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Iceland%20entering%20a%20new%20volcanic%20era%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707529921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA26C%2Fproduction%2F_132608514_8d552d9e1758a87258dc0d861ee6d6e4542305e1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68255375%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20think%20eruptions%20on%20the%20Reykjanes%20Peninsula%20could%20continue%20for%20decades%20or%20even%20centuries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A508%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68255375%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68255375.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68255375.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Fiscal%20Injustice'%20Powers%20a%20New%20Axis%20of%20Protest%20Against%20Modi%20Govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09211831%2FFotoJet-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20simmering%20fault%20line%20between%20BJP-led%20Centre%20and%20non-BJP%20governments%20in%20states%20came%20to%20a%20boil%20this%20week.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20led%20an%20agitation%20against%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cfinancial%20injustice%E2%80%9D%20towards%20Karnataka.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20staged%20a%20similar%20protest%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVijayan%20was%20also%20accompanied%20by%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20his%20Punjab%20counterpart%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20and%20DMK%20minister%20P.%20Thiagarajan.%20The%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20YSR%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20and%20M.K.Stalin%2C%20also%20protested%20against%20the%20unfair%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20states%20that%20have%20contributed%20the%20most%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20exchequer.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20all%20these%20states%20have%20taken%20to%20popular%20protests%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20moving%20the%20question%20of%20partisanship%20over%20resources%20out%20of%20discussion%20rooms.%20The%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi-led%20Telangana%20government%20had%20also%20agitated%20over%20the%20issue%20in%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20argument%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20governments%20are%20demanding%20that%20their%20share%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20states%20by%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20should%20be%20greater%20than%20what%20they%20currently%20receive%2C%20given%20their%20share%20of%20contribution%20to%20the%20exchequer%20is%20also%20greater%20than%20most%20other%20states%20who%20receive%20a%20better%20share.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20have%20said%20that%20even%20the%20mandated%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20has%20not%20been%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%2C%20and%20has%20created%20a%20backlog%20in%20the%20development%20goals%20of%20the%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20allied%20issues%2C%20too.%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20alleged%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20not%20released%20special%20grants%20worth%20Rs%205495%20crores%2C%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20and%20also%20denied%20the%20promised%20grant%20of%20around%20Rs%206000%20crores%20for%20drought-hit%20Karnataka%20which%20it%20could%20have%20used%20for%20infrastructure%20development%20of%20water%20bodies%20and%20irrigation%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Finance%20Commission%20is%20the%20Constitutional%20body%20to%20devise%20a%20formula%20for%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20demographic%20performance%2C%20demographic%20performance%2C%20area%2C%20income%20distance%2C%20tax%20and%20fiscal%20efforts%2C%20forest%20cover%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20highest%20weightage%20is%20given%20to%20the%20population%20of%20states%2C%20which%20has%20meant%20that%20states%20which%20have%20been%20able%20to%20contain%20their%20population%20spiral%20eventually%20end%20up%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ladder%20of%20beneficiaries.%20The%20southern%20states%20have%20historically%20done%20better%20than%20north%20Indian%20states%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20criteria%20of%20development%20indices%20and%20emerged%20as%20the%20highest%20contributors%20of%20taxes%20to%20the%20exchequer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20their%20share%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20is%20the%20least.%20The%20charts%20shared%20on%20X%20by%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20P.Wilson%20post%20on%20X%20gives%20a%20fair%20idea%20of%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPlease%20find%20the%20flow%20chart%20provided%20below%20to%20assist%20with%20better%20understanding.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBJPLootingOurTax%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BJPLootingOurTax%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F089YuHP7O3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F089YuHP7O3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20P.%20Wilson%20(%40PWilsonDMK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPWilsonDMK%2Fstatus%2F1755566669630509322%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20finance%20commission%E2%80%99s%20formula%20has%20dis-incentivised%20states%20to%20excel%2C%20as%20that%20may%20also%20result%20in%20a%20dramatic%20slashing%20of%20their%20share%20in%20tax%20revenues.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMaharashtra%20shares%20Rs%201%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20it%20is%20eligible%20to%20get%20back%20only%20Rs%200.08%20paise.%20Similarly%2C%20Karnataka%20will%20get%20back%20Rs%200.15%20paise%2C%20while%20Gujarat%20will%20receive%20Rs%200.08%20paise%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Rs%200.29%20paise.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20states%20whose%20governments%20have%20performed%20poorly%20to%20control%20their%20population%20and%20made%20least%20tax%20and%20fiscal%20effort%20get%20the%20maximum%20share%20of%20tax%20revenues.%20Thus%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20gets%20Rs%202.73%20for%20every%20rupee%20it%20shares%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20while%20Bihar%20gets%20Rs%207.06.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20southern%20states%20have%20performed%20better%20than%20most%20others%20on%20all%20fronts%2C%20while%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20Vindhyas%2C%20only%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Haryana%20match%20up%20to%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anomaly%20stands%20to%20only%20deepen%20with%20subsequent%20census%20exercises%2C%20and%20is%20crying%20out%20to%20be%20addressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%20increased%20the%20vertical%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20states%20to%2042%25%2C%20while%20the%2015th%2C%20currently%20in%20action%2C%20decreased%20it%20by%201%25%20to%2041%25%20However%2C%20the%20subsequent%20horizontal%20devolution%20is%20where%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20are%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pyramid%20as%20far%20as%20their%20contribution%20to%20the%20central%20pool%20is%20concerned%2C%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20getting%20a%20poor%20deal.%20To%20placate%20states%20which%20have%20performed%20historically%20well%2C%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20recommended%20special%20grants%2C%20which%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20said%20to%20have%20not%20received%2C%20and%20termed%20it%20as%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice%E2%80%9D%20towards%20non-BJP%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Centre%2C%20however%2C%20has%20denied%20all%20charges.%20The%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20her%20ministry%20has%20processed%20all%20dues%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rules%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20protesting%20governments%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20Finance%20Commission%20instead%20of%20demonstrating%20against%20the%20Centre.%20But%20she%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20question%20of%20special%20grants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20machinery%20has%20gone%20ahead%20to%20canvas%20that%20the%20non-BJP%20governments%20are%20attempting%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20along%20North-South%20lines%20and%20that%20the%20protests%20advocate%20separatism%20and%20even%20a%20split%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20accusation%20and%20said%20that%20India%20is%20a%20united%20country%2C%20but%20argued%20that%20Karnataka%20has%20continued%20to%20get%20a%20poor%20deal%20over%20the%20years.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20was%20promised%20a%20drought%20relief%20package%20by%20both%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20which%20has%20still%20not%20been%20finalised%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20223%20of%20the%20236%20taluks%20of%20the%20state%20are%20reeling%20under%20conditions%20of%20a%20severe%20drought.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20is%20demanding%20its%20just%20GST%20dues%20and%20special%20grants%20that%20have%20still%20not%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20while%20also%20appealing%20to%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%20of%20fixing%20a%20more%20fair%20deal%20for%20states%20which%20are%20taking%20the%20effort%20to%20improve%20conditions%20in%20the%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%20had%20fixed%20the%20share%20of%20taxes%20for%20Karnataka%20at%204.71%25%2C%20while%20the%2015th%20decreased%20it%20further%20to%203.65%25%2C%20representing%20a%20speculative%20loss%20of%20around%201.87%20lakh%20crores.%20%E2%80%9CPut%20together%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20losses%20amount%20to%20around%20Rs%2062%2C098%20crore.%20Should%20we%20keep%20quiet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20protest%20was%20for%20Karnataka%20and%20its%20people%2C%20and%20that%20he%20had%20also%20invited%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20its%20Karnataka%20leaders%20like%20Tejaswi%20Surya%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20Pratap%20Simha%20and%20others%20to%20join%20the%20cause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%20to%20decide%20states%E2%80%99%20share%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%201971%20Census%20to%20prevent%20such%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice%E2%80%9D%20towards%20Karnataka%20which%20has%20controlled%20its%20population%20through%20better%20implementation%20of%20birth%20control%20and%20economic%20parity%20measures%20over%20the%20years.%20Why%20should%20we%20be%20penalised%20for%20doing%20our%20work%20sincerely%2C%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20also%20alleged%20that%20it%20has%20not%20received%20dues%20worth%20Rs%2057%2C400%20crores%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal.%20Citing%20figures%20from%20a%20RBI%20report%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20continuously%20not%20met%20the%20requirements%20of%20even%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunjust%E2%80%9D%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20opposition-ruled%20states.%20It%20said%20that%20it%20was%20denied%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%20this%20year%20scheduled%20to%20have%20come%20from%20GST%20compensation%20from%20June%202022.%C2%A0%20Chief%20minister%20Vijayan%20said%20that%20while%20Kerala%20received%203.87%25%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20during%20the%20period%20of%2010th%20finance%20commission%2C%20it%20came%20down%20to%202.5%25%20in%20the%2014th%20and%201.925%25%20in%20the%2015th%20finance%20commission%2C%20leading%20to%20huge%20losses%20for%20the%20state%20every%20subsequent%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20grieving%20states%20have%20complained%20about%20the%20Centre%20releasing%20only%20an%20average%20of%20only%2035%25%20as%20share%20to%20the%20states%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20mandated%2041%25%20recommended%20by%20the%2015th%20finance%20commission.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20said%20that%20the%20special%20grants%20as%20capital%20expenditure%20and%20capacity%20of%20states%20to%20borrow%20have%20also%20taken%20a%20hit%20because%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%E2%80%9D%20devolution%20process.%20The%20anomalies%20in%20the%20promised%20GST%20compensation%20and%20failure%20to%20disburse%20the%20recommended%20special%20grants%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20states%20have%20only%20escalated%20anger%20among%20opposition%20parties.%20They%20also%20believe%20that%20the%20share%20of%20tax%20revenue%20collected%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccess%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Csurcharge%E2%80%9D%20has%20grown%20dramatically%20during%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20from%2010%25%20during%20the%20UPA%20era%20to%20over%2026%25%20now%2C%20but%20is%20not%20shared%20with%20the%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAsking%20for%20their%20due%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20charge%20that%20the%20opposition-ruled%20states%20are%20trying%20to%20balkanise%20India%20lacks%20merit%20against%20such%20a%20backdrop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20states%20like%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Gujarat%20and%20Haryana%20face%20the%20same%20problem%20and%20have%20raised%20their%20voices%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Given%20the%20criteria%20of%20devolution%20and%20future%20census%20exercises%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20poorly-performing%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20which%20receive%20the%20highest%20share%20of%20taxes%20despite%20contributing%20the%20least%2C%20may%20only%20increase.%20This%20may%20lead%20to%20further%20escalation%20of%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEconomists%20have%20long%20debated%20the%20issue.%20While%20some%20believe%20that%20the%20weightage%20of%20population%20could%20be%20decreased%20to%20prevent%20future%20fights%20between%20states%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20some%20say%20that%20the%20devolution%20formula%20could%20be%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20one%20of%20the%20pre-2011%20census%20data.%20Many%20others%20believe%20that%20a%20variable%20component%20could%20be%20introduced%20that%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20efforts%20made%20by%20states%20to%20close%20the%20huge%20gap%20between%20states%2C%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Bihar%2C%20and%20given%20more%20weightage%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes.%20They%20say%20that%20if%20the%20effort%20by%20states%20is%20not%20visible%2C%20then%20the%20whole%20purpose%20of%20supporting%20poor%20states%20to%20bring%20them%20at%20par%20with%20those%20with%20a%20good%20track%20record%20is%20defeated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tussle%20over%20%E2%80%9Cfiscal%20injustice%E2%80%9D%20has%20already%20begun%20to%20intensify%20the%20politics%20around%20it.%20This%20has%20made%20the%20Modi%20government%20uncomfortable%20as%20it%20is%20an%20agenda%20set%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20that%20Modi%20knows%20will%20divert%20from%20issues%20he%20wants%20to%20fight%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20seen%20usually%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98soft%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20more%20anti-Congress%20than%20anti-Centre%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20no%20political%20party%20should%20get%20a%20full%20majority%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20that%20only%20a%20coalition%20government%20can%20meet%20the%20aspirations%20of%20varied%20democratic%20voices%20within%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequent%20finance%20commissions%20and%20the%20central%20government%20will%20have%20to%20eventually%20address%20the%20uneven%20situation%20at%