0now%20on%20the%20other%20foot%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20contractors'%20body%20which%20had%20alleged%20that%2040%25%20commission%20had%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20get%20contracts%20for%20public%20projects%20under%20the%20Basavaraj%20Bommai-led%20BJP%20government%20has%20levelled%20the%20same%20allegation%20at%20the%20Congress%20government%20which%20came%20to%20power%20last%20year%2C%20but%20with%20a%20twist.%20The%20association%20has%20said%20that%20instead%20of%20politicians%20making%20money%2C%20it%20is%20bureaucrats%20who%20are%20doing%20so%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attack%20the%20Congress%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20said%20the%20contractors'%20body%20must%20present%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association's%20allegations%20in%202022%20had%20led%20to%20the%20Congress%20terming%20the%20BJP%20regime%20in%20the%20state%20a%20'40%25%20sarkara'%20(40%25%20government).%20The%20party%20also%20launched%20a%20'PayCM'%20campaign%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20leading%20to%20a%20'40%25%20sarkara'%20website%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20was%20charging%2040%25%20commission%20on%20public%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20had%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20Congress%20storming%20back%20to%20power%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20winning%20135%20of%20224%20Assembly%20seats.%20The%20claims%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20have%20come%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED%20Kempanna%2C%20President%2C%20Karnataka%20State%20Contractors'%20Association%2C%20who%20had%20complained%20about%20corruption%20in%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20corruption%20has%20come%20down.%20Now%2C%20officials%20are%20making%20money.%20Earlier%2C%20politicians%20were.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20members%20of%20the%20association%20alleged%20that%20officials%20don't%20issue%20work%20orders%20or%20release%20money%20unless%20bribes%20are%20paid%20and%20also%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bpackage%20deals%26quot%3B%20are%20awarded%20to%20agencies%20close%20to%20the%20bureaucrats%2C%20ignoring%20local%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20asked%20Mr%20Kempanna%20to%20approach%20Justice%20Nagamohan%20Das%20Commission%20if%20he%20has%20documents%20to%20prove%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20constituted%20the%20Justice%20Nagamohan%20Das%20Commission%20to%20probe%20'40%20per%20cent%20commission'%20that%20happened%20in%20the%20previous%20(BJP)%20government.%20If%20he%20has%20documents%20then%20he%20must%20share%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Siddaramaiah%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Industries%20Minister%20MB%20Patil%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20him%20(Mr%20Kempanna)%20state%20the%20departments...%20present%20facts%20against%20Bruhat%20Bengaluru%20Mahanagara%20Palike%20(Bengaluru%20municipal%20corporation)%20or%20the%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board...%20and%20not%20make%20general%20statements.%20If%20there%20is%20anything%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20will%20inquire%20into%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20corruption%26quot%3B%20has%20now%20been%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20party%20made%20false%20allegations%20against%20our%20government.%20Now%2C%20the%20real%20corruption%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20Congress%20government.%20Now%20the%20same%20contractors%2C%20who%20are%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20are%20feeling%20the%20heat%20and%20facing%20the%20music%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20MLA%20CN%20Ashwath%20Narayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707493080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2Fr5kv4fag_paycm-protest-ndtv-650_650x400_