perature%20is%20stringently%20controlled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20threads%20are%20the%20stigma%20of%20the%20flower%20that%20are%20harvested%20and%20dried%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-2-1707479222-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20saffron%20threads%20are%20the%20stigma%20of%20the%20flower%20that%20are%20harvested%20and%20dried%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-3-1707479405.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taking%20out%20the%20stigmas%20from%20the%20flower%20is%20a%20manual%20time-consuming%20process%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-3-1707479405.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-3-1707479405-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-3-1707479405-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-3-1707479405-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-3-1707479405-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341329%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaking%20out%20the%20stigmas%20from%20the%20flower%20is%20a%20manual%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aim%20is%20to%20mimic%20the%20climes%20of%20the%20Valley%2C%20as%20the%20seeds%20only%20flower%20at%20a%20specific%20temperature.%20Elaborating%20on%20how%20they%20managed%20to%20achieve%20this%2C%20Vaibhav%20says%20%E2%80%9CThe%20temperature%20in%20the%20room%20has%20to%20be%20decreased%20gradually%20just%20as%20if%20winter%20is%20coming%20to%20Kashmir.%20We%E2%80%99re%20essentially%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20seeds%20feel%20at%20home.%20So%2C%20we%20start%20at%2025%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20gradually%20drop%20the%20temperature%20to%20five%20degrees%20through%20the%20next%20four%20months%20until%20harvest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%204%3A%20Pluck%20the%20flowers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purple%20bloom%20conveys%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276908%2Fdehradun-gardener-flower-plants-how-to-garden-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20harvest%20is%20ready%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Each%20flower%20comprises%20petals%2C%20the%20stamen%20and%20the%20stigma.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20of%20these%20parts%20has%20a%20different%20use.%20The%20petals%20are%20used%20in%20the%20cosmetic%20industry%2C%20the%20yellow%20stamen%20is%20used%20in%20the%20textile%20industry%20for%20dyeing%2C%20and%20the%20stigma%20is%20the%20red%20saffron.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%205%3A%20Place%20the%20seeds%20back%20into%20the%20soil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20flowers%20have%20been%20plucked%20out%2C%20all%20the%20seeds%20are%20placed%20back%20into%20the%20soil%20so%20they%20can%20flower%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20cycle%20that%20began%20on%2015%20August%20was%20completed%20on%201%20November%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEnsure%20that%20you%20water%20the%20seeds%20every%207%20to%2010%20days%2C%20and%20not%20exceed%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%20Once%20it%E2%80%99s%20August%2C%20the%20flowers%20will%20be%20harvested%20again.%20%E2%80%9CThus%2C%20you%20see%2C%20each%20bulb%20has%20a%20lifetime%20of%20a%20decade%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F17686%2F5-secrets-to-the-most-amazing-terrace-garden-from-expert-viswanath-kadur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20saffron%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20one-time%20investment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20history%20loves%20this%20%E2%80%98red%20gold%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20one%20spice%20that%20is%20history%E2%80%99s%20favourite%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20saffron.%20Legends%20tell%20of%20how%20Cleopatra%20bathed%20with%20it%20and%20Alexander%20the%20Great%20used%20it%20to%20heal%20battle%20wounds.%20Price%20is%20no%20bar%20it%20seems%20as%20some%20traders%20in%20Kashmir%20get%20a%20handsome%20Rs%202%20lakh%20per%20kg%20according%20to%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20spice%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20every%20country%E2%80%99s%20cup%20of%20tea.%20Iran%20produces%2095%20percent%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20saffron%20and%20Kashmir%20a%20great%20margin%20too.%20The%20spice%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20certain%20climate%20means%20not%20every%20country%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332547%2Fsooraj-purushothaman-organic-farmer-kerala-gardening-growing-vegetables%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavourable%20for%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20it%20takes%20one%20lakh%20flowers%20to%20produce%20one%20kg%20of%20saffron%20(and%20the%20entire%20process%20must%20be%20done%20by%20hand)%20adds%20to%20its%20expense.%20And%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20have%20mastered%20the%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-4-1707479491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Once%20the%20flowers%20have%20been%20plucked%20the%20seeds%20are%20put%20into%20the%20soil%20once%20more%20for%20the%20next%20harvest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-4-1707479491.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-4-1707479491-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-4-1707479491-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-4-1707479491-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-4-1707479491-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341330%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOnce%20the%20flowers%20have%20been%20plucked%20the%20seeds%20are%20put%20into%20the%20soil%20once%20more%20for%20the%20next%20harvest%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aastha%20and%20Vaibhav%20Patel%20have%20started%20growing%20saffron%20in%20their%20Vadodara%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341331%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAastha%20and%20Vaibhav%20Patel%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%205%2C707%20hectares%20of%20land%20under%20saffron%20cultivation%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20is%20in%20the%20Pampore%20tehsil%20of%20Pulwama%20district%20in%20South%20Kashmir.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20Valley%20rejoiced%20as%20the%20GI%20tag%20was%20given%20to%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20making%20it%20illegal%20for%20someone%20outside%20the%20valley%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20a%20similar%20product%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20saffron%E2%80%99%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20grown%20in%20the%20Valley%20is%20of%20three%20types%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Lachha%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20just%20separated%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329424%2Fludhiana-woman-grows-200-plants-in-terrace-garden-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flowers%20are%20dried%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20further%20processing%3B%20%E2%80%98Mongra%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20are%20detached%20from%20the%20flower%2C%20dried%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20and%20processed%20traditionally%3B%20and%20%E2%80%98Guchhi%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20which%20also%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20stigmas%20being%20processed.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20dried%20and%20joined%20in%20a%20bundle%20tied%20with%20a%20cloth%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20that%20the%20Patels%20are%20growing%20is%20the%20second%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20harvest%20was%20an%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20emphasises.%20But%20lucrative%20all%20the%20same.%20Each%20gram%20of%20the%20red%20threads%20fetched%20the%20couple%20Rs%20700.%20As%20for%20the%20road%20ahead%2C%20they%20are%20confident%20they%20can%20expand%20sales%20implementing%20the%20learnings%20of%20the%20previous%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707485452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_0318_11zon-1707478888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20to%20grow%20saffron%20at%20home%3F%20Vaibhav%20Patel%20and%20Aastha%20Maheshwari%20Patel%20have%20transformed%20their%20Vadodara%20home%20into%20a%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20haven%2C%20defying%20geographical%20norms.%20They%20share%20insights%20into%20the%20intricate%20process%20of%20growing%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20spice%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20Fitting%20Tribute%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20WHO%20Chief%20Scientist%20On%20Bharat%20Ratna%20To%20Father%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20is%20very%20happy%20and%20delighted%20with%20the%20honour%2C%20said%20Dr%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%2C%20former%20chief%20scientist%20of%20WHO%20and%20the%20daughter%20of%20noted%20agricultural%20scientist%20MS%20Swaminathan%20who%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNaturally%20we%20are%20very%20happy%2C%20delighted%20and%20feel%20honoured%20that%20he%20has%20been%20honoured%20with%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20of%20the%20country%20that%20is%20given%20to%20the%20country's%20most%20eminent%20citizens.%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20fitting%20tribute%20for%20somebody%20who%20spent%20his%20whole%20life%20working%20for%20the%20country.%20So%20it's%20a%20very%20happy%20and%20wonderful%20day%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20award%20comes%20just%20months%20after%20MS%20Swaminathan's%20death%20in%20September%202023.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20passed%20away%20just%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20and%20I'm%20sure%20that%20he%20would've%20been%20truly%20very%2C%20very%20happy%20if%20he%20had%20the%20news%20during%20his%20lifetime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20his%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20what%20it%20is.%20It%20is%20a%20recognition%20of%20the%20work%20that%20he%20has%20done%20and%20I%20think%20more%20than%20anything%20else%20it's%20a%20very%20strong%20signal%20that%20the%20country%20respects%20and%20rewards%20its%20scientists%2C%20especially%20agricultural%20scientists%20who%20are%20often%20not%20in%20the%20limelight%20but%20are%20so%20important%20-%20were%20in%20the%20past%20and%20will%20be%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20award%2C%20announced%20just%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP's%20way%20of%20wooing%20the%20south%3F%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20frankly%20I'm%20not%20even%20thinking%20about%20those%20things.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20politics%20here%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20tribute%20to%20an%20individual.%20It's%20a%20tribute%20to%20my%20father%20and%20you%20know%20we%20have%20seen%20from%20childhood...%20He%20had%20an%20amazing%20ability%20-%20whether%20it%20was%20farmers%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20country%20or%20whether%20it%20was%20politicians%20or%20whether%20it%20was%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20Nobel%20laureates%2C%20he%20was%20equally%20at%20home%20in%20all%20of%20the%20settings%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20that%20special%20gift%20he%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20the%20Padma%20awards%2C%20they%20come%20from%20all%20over%20India...%20My%20father%20never%20considered%20himself%20to%20particularly%20belong%20to%20any%20one%20state%20or%20community.%20I%20think%20he%20really%20was%20an%20Indian.%20He%20belonged%20to%20the%20Gandhian%20era.%20He%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20era%20of%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20for%20him%2C%20the%20country%20was%20above%20everything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20two%20former%20PMs%20-%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20-%20and%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20matter%20of%20immense%20joy%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20announced%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20for%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20and%20said%20the%20honour%20was%20being%20conferred%20on%20the%20scientist%20%26quot%3Bin%20recognition%20of%20his%20monumental%20contributions%20to%20our%20nation%20in%20agriculture%20and%20farmers'%20welfare%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707485340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F4cgvdl_soumya-swaminathan_625x300_02_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2