tps%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20a%20permanent%20commission%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20gender%20discrimination.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20a%20permanent%20commission%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20gender%20discrimination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Kargil%20war%20veteran%20(who%20prefers%20to%20remain%20anonymous)%20who%20joined%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%201996%2C%20says%20she%20was%20%E2%80%98released%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20service%20after%20a%20total%20of%2012%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20experience%20in%20the%20IAF%2C%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20underwent%20the%20exact%20same%20training%20of%20one%20year%20along%20with%20male%20cadets.%20We%20never%20took%20help%20from%20anyone%20in%20doing%20our%20duty%20or%20task%2C%20be%20it%20night%20guard%20patrol%20check%20duty%20or%20any%20other%20professional%20task.%20My%20trainer%20said%20no%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that%20we%20were%20less%20than%20any%20male%20counterpart.%20And%20I%20ensured%20that%20no%20one%20could%20point%20out%20anything%20just%20because%20I%20am%20a%20female.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20individual%20officers%20are%20good%20but%20female%20officers%20in%20general%20were%20treated%20like%20guinea%20pigs%20%E2%80%93%20experimented%20on%20and%20then%20thrown%20away.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20IAF%20and%20serve%20for%20more%20years%2C%20just%20like%20my%20male%20counterparts%2C%20but%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20raise%20this%20issue%2C%2032%20female%20officers%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20court%20and%20in%202003%2C%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20was%20instituted%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20titled%20%E2%80%98Babita%20Puniya%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20permanent%20commission%20to%20women%20SSC%20Officers%E2%80%99%2C%20highlighting%20the%20gender%20discrimination%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20struggle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20stated%20that%20the%20Permanent%20Commission%20shall%20be%20offered%20to%20women%20officers%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20five%20years%2C%20subject%20to%20vacancies%20and%20suitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judgment%20was%20said%20to%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20only%20those%20officers%20who%20were%20in%20service%20or%20those%20retired%2Freleased%20officers%20who%20were%20not%20in%20service%20as%20on%2012%20March%202010%20but%20had%20filed%20writ%20petitions%20before%20their%20release%20%E2%80%93%20a%20criterion%20that%20did%20not%20match%20with%20the%20appellants%20and%20hence%20they%20were%20left%20out%20from%20the%20reinstatement%20plan%20of%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20immediately%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20challenging%20the%20manner%20of%20implementation%20of%20the%20decision%20in%20Babita%20Puniya%E2%80%99s%20case%20by%20the%20IAF.%20However%2C%20by%20an%20order%20dated%2027%20September%202011%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20review%20petitions%20filed%20against%20the%20impugned%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20officers%20joined%20the%20service%20between%201993%20and%201998%20and%20were%20eventually%20released%20from%20service%20between%20December%202006%20and%202009.%20As%20these%20female%20officers%20put%20in%20long%20years%20of%20service%20for%20the%20IAF%2C%20the%20lawyers%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20they%20should%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20pensionary%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20team%20of%20lawyers%2C%20including%20Garima%20Sachdeva%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202022%20directed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F70596%2Ffirst-officers-indian-air-force-harjinder-singh-jumbo-majumdar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Air%20Force%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20consider%20granting%20pensionary%20benefits%20to%2032%20retired%20female%20SSC%20officers%20deeming%20they%20had%20permanent%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20was%20finally%20put%20to%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1-1707394965.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Garima%20opines%20that%20those%2032%20women%20have%20set%20a%20benchmark%20for%20other%20female%20officers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1-1707394965.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1-1707394965-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1-1707394965-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1-1707394965-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1-1707394965-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341174%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGarima%20opines%20that%20those%2032%20women%20have%20set%20a%20benchmark%20for%20other%20female%20officers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kargil%20war%20veteran%20(who%20prefers%20to%20remain%20anonymous)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20who%20gave%20us%20justice%20and%20sadly%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20the%20organisation%20which%20is%20still%20our%20first%20love%20%E2%80%94%20the%20IAF.%20We%20fought%20our%20battle%20up%20to%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20justice%20and%20won%20against%20IAF.%20The%20decision%20has%20given%20me%20mental%20peace.%20Now%2C%20I%20await%20my%20pensionary%20benefits%20that%20are%20in%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarima%20opines%20that%20these%2032%20women%20have%20set%20a%20benchmark%20for%20other%20female%20officers.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20matter%20went%20on%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20see%20how%20these%20women%20officers%20who%20fought%20for%20so%20long%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20get%20any%20tangible%20satisfaction%20out%20of%20it.%20The%20only%20satisfaction%20was%20that%20they%20won%20and%20they%20set%20up%20a%20benchmark%20for%20all%20the%20coming%20generations%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Garima%2C%20the%20court%20order%20gave%20her%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20pride%20and%20strength.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20Air%20Force%20background%2C%20I%20had%20my%20heart%20and%20soul%20in%20this%20matter.%20I%20was%20happy%20that%20I%20could%20get%20the%20best%20out%20of%20my%20capabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20nothing%20beats%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20fighting%20for%20women%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20systems%20and%20emerging%20victorious%20for%20those%20who%20have%20high%20hopes%20in%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Garima%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20appointed%20as%20a%20Senior%20Panel%20Counsel%20at%20both%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Principal%20Bench%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20Tribunal.%20She%20currently%20represents%20the%20armed%20forces%20before%20these%20forums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Garima%20Sachdeva)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707460807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20Advocate%20Garima%20Sachdeva%20shares%20how%20she%20fought%20for%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20on%20invading%20Poland%2C%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20American%20'spies'%20and%20Russia%20joining%20NATO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707439680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-vladimir-putin-tucker-carlson_6449231.jpg%3F20240209071146%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fputin-claims-clinton-misled-him-over-russias-potential-membership-of-nato-13067162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20said%20Bill%20Clinton%20misled%20him%20over%20Russia's%20potential%20membership%20of%20NATO%20two%20decades%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A792%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fputin-claims-clinton-misled-him-over-russias-potential-membership-of-nato-13067162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fputin-claims-clinton-misled-him-over-russias