uring%20the%20winter%20season%2C%20as%20the%20Delhi%20resident%20observed%20his%20family%20donating%20blankets%20to%20the%20underprivileged%20on%20the%20streets.%20Nirvaan%20recognised%20that%20blankets%20offered%20only%20a%20short-term%20solution%20and%20might%20not%20endure%20the%20harsh%20winters%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%3A%20repurposing%20old%20denim%20to%20create%20sleeping%20bags.%20This%20initiative%20not%20only%20prevented%20jeans%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%20but%20also%20offered%20a%20durable%20and%20warm%20sleeping%20option%20for%20the%20homeless%20during%20freezing%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202022%2C%20%E2%80%98Project%20Jeans%20%E2%80%94%20Blue%20To%20Green%E2%80%99%20has%20distributed%20over%202%2C000%20sleeping%20bags%20across%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Himachal%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20even%20Turkey%20and%20Syria%20by%20recycling%20over%2012%2C000%20jeans%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20warm%20hug%20on%20cold%20winter%20nights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sleeping%20bag%20made%20by%20Project%20Jeans%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-300x146.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-500x243.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-768x373.jpeg%20768