iming%20to%20replace%20physical%20weights%20with%20digital%20ones%20using%20motors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20replicate%20the%20same%20types%20of%20resistance%20that%20a%20physical%20weight%20provides%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20motor%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20four%20of%20them%20worked%20on%20building%20prototypes%2C%20investing%20almost%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20of%20their%20own%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Aroleap%20X%20comes%20with%20over%20150%20exercises%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740-272x182.jpg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340985%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Aroleap%20X%20comes%20with%20over%20150%20exercises.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20they%20incorporated%20their%20company%20by%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Aroleap%20Fitness%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99.%20Amid