0become%20their%20first%20angel%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20found%20three%20other%20investors%20and%20raised%20their%20seed%20capital%20in%20October%202021.%20Then%2C%20they%20set%20up%20a%20small%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20began%20selling%20Aroleap%20X%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20home%20gym%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Aroleap%20(%40aroleap)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAroleap%20X%20is%20a%20compact%2C%20wall-mounted%20smart%20exercise%20machine%20that%20uses%20motor-powered%20electromagnetic%20resistances%20to%20provide%20a%20data-driven%20workout.%20The%20device%20takes%20up%204%20feet%20x%202%20feet%20space%2C%20which%20is%20equivalent%20to%20a%20vertically%20wall-mounted%2055%20inch%20LED%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20patented%20digital-weights%20technology%20was%20built%20in-house%20and%20comes%20with%20fitness%20content%20to%20support%20workouts.%20The%20machine%20uses%20a%20motor%20to%20simulate%20the%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20pull%20the%20rope%20on%20the%20device%2C%20it%20generates%20resistance.%20Our%20device%20works%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322864%2Fkochi-aathira-sethumadhavan-pcos-weight-loss-healthy-diet-nutrition-sustainable-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20trainer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tells%20you%20when%20to%20reduce%20or%20increase%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20can%20be%20used%20to%20do%20everything%20that%20you%20do%20at%20a%20gym%2C%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20technology%20has%20condensed%20all%20different%20weight%20stacks%20into%20a%20single%20motor.%20We%20have%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20motor-controlled%20technology.%20Our%20motor%20provides%20resistance%20from%202%20kg%20to%2075%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20150%20exercises%20can%20be%20done%20using%20the%20machine%2C%20and%20every%20muscle%20group%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20body%20can%20be%20targeted.%20AI-powered%20training%20sessions%20track%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20progress%20and%20suggest%20better%20methods%20of%20working%20out%2C%20while%20giving%20real-time%20tracking%20and%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20offers%20goal-based%20workout%20programmes%2C%20designed%20by%20professional%20fitness%20trainers.%20From%20building%20muscle%20and%20weight%20training%20to%20becoming%20a%20better%20runner%2C%20the%20machine%20has%20something%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20comes%20with%20two%20arms%2C%20which%20can%20be%20adjusted%20at%20differ