%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20utilising%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20would%20just%20explain%20concepts%2C%20with%20children%20not%20being%20able%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works.%20Through%20these%20models%20and%20kits%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20the%20concept%20works%2C%20helping%20in%20easier%20understanding.%20Children%20also%20ask%20more%20questions.%20The%20concept%20reaches%20them%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Veeramuthu%20N%2C%20a%20teacher%20from%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kaliannanpudur%2C%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20provided%20them%20with%2075%20kits%2C%20which%20include%20working%20models%2C%20explanatory%20models%20and%20charts.%20Children%20are%20taken%20to%20the%20lab%2C%20where%20they%20can%20experiment.%20Alternatively%2C%20teachers%20also%20bring%20the%20models%20to%20class%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20concept%20they%20are%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20NGO%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20American%20India%20Foundation%20(AIF)%20and%20Don%20Bosco%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%94%20offer%20after-school%20classes%20for%20students.%20These%20sessions%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%2C%20including%20mobile%20application%20development%2C%20coding%2C%20CNC%20machining%2C%20sensors%2C%20map%20making%2C%203D%20printing%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20knowledge%20gained%20in%20these%20classes%20empowers%20children%20to%20apply%20these%20concepts%20to%20solve%20real-life%20problems%20they%20encounter%20in%20their%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFiring%20the%20creativity%20in%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240