0only%20two%20years%20old%20when%20he%20lost%20his%20father.%20Growing%20up%20fatherless%20came%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20issues%20but%20one%20of%20them%20was%20bringing%20food%20to%20the%20table.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20raised%20me%20and%20my%20elder%20sister%20all%20on%20her%20own.%20We%20often%20went%20to%20bed%20hungry%20and%20famished%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20the%20Milaap%20Foundation%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20what%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277456%2Fmillet-man-of-telangana-veer-shetty-biradar-ss-bhavani-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehunger%20and%20helplessness%20%3C%2Fa%3Efeels%20like%2C%20when%20Deepankar%20started%20to%20earn%20an%20income%2C%20he%20started%20taking%20some%20time%20out%20to%20deliver%20food%20to%20the%20senior%20citizens%20of%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20give%20up%20his%20career%20and%20dedicate%20all%20his%20time%20to%20serving%20others.%20Treating%20all%20the%20elderly%20people%20like%20his%20grandparents%2C%20Deepankar%20has%20provided%20thousands%20of%20free%20meals%20through%20his%20foundation%2C%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20very%20sick%20once%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Edadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20told%20me%20that%20a%20person%20who%20feeds%20hundreds%20need%20to%20be%20alive%20for%20as%20long%20as%20he%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20love%20he%20receives%20from%20these%20seniors%20keeps%20him%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707137028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340768%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepankar%20Patil%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98Art%20of%20Helping%20Foundation%E2%80%99%20in%20Pune%2C%20quit%20his%20job%20as%20a%20graphic%20designer%20to%20help%20senior%20citiz