e%20of%20visa%20issues%20or%20marriage.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20a%20single%20woman%20follow%20her%20passions%3F%20Why%20is%20getting%20married%20the%20only%20way%20to%20settle%20down%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20women%20is%20to%20have%20a%20good%20education%20and%20be%20financially%20independent.%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20be%20unstoppable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20lucky%20because%20my%20mother%20gave%20me%20that%20opportunity%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20gets%20it.%20Women%20leaders%20have%20the%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20jobs%20to%20other%20women.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20create%20an%20equal%20world%20for%20young%20girls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20Secret%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20Ahana%E2%80%99s%20love%20letter%20to%20her%20single%20mother%2C%20who%20showed%20her%20daughter%20that%20nothing%20is%20impossible.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98open%20secret%E2%80%99%20that%20we%20are%20who%20we%20are%20because%20of%20our%20mothers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20proud%20daughter%20dedicating%20her%20brand%20to%20all%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ahana%E2%80%99s%20mother%20saw%20her%20daughter%20open%20her%20wings%20and%20fly%2C%20she%20passed%20away%20during%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20in%202021.%20Ahana%20had%20to%20make%20a%20tough%20choice%20the%20next%20day%20as%20she%20had%20an%20investor%20meeting%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20either%20pause%20and%20grieve%2C%20or%20pitch%20to%20the%20investor%20for%20our%20Series%20A%20round%2C%20and%20I%20chose%20the%20latter%2C%20as%20I%20had%20to%20build%20this%20brand%20and%20keep%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20alive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707134492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340611%22%2C%22summary%22